    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "mn132:1.1",
          "pli": "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—",
          "en": "So I have heard. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:1.2",
          "pli": "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. ",
          "en": "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:2.1",
          "pli": "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā ānando upaṭṭhānasālāyaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandasseti samādapeti samuttejeti sampahaṃseti, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca vibhaṅgañca bhāsati. ",
          "en": "Now at that time Venerable Ānanda was educating, encouraging, firing up, and inspiring the mendicants in the assembly hall with a Dhamma talk on the topic of the recitation passage and analysis of One Fine Night. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:2.2",
          "pli": "Atha kho bhagavā sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yenupaṭṭhānasālā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi. ",
          "en": "Then in the late afternoon, the Buddha came out of retreat, went to the assembly hall, where he sat on the seat spread out, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:2.3",
          "pli": "Nisajja kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi: ",
          "en": "and addressed the mendicants, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:2.4",
          "pli": "“ko nu kho, bhikkhave, upaṭṭhānasālāyaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassesi samādapesi samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca vibhaṅgañca abhāsī”ti? ",
          "en": "“Who was inspiring the mendicants with a talk on the recitation passage and analysis of One Fine Night?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:2.5",
          "pli": "“Āyasmā, bhante, ānando upaṭṭhānasālāyaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassesi samādapesi samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca vibhaṅgañca abhāsī”ti. ",
          "en": "“It was Venerable Ānanda, sir.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:2.6",
          "pli": "Atha kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ āmantesi: ",
          "en": "Then the Buddha said to Venerable Ānanda, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:2.7",
          "pli": "“yathā kathaṃ pana tvaṃ, ānanda, bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassesi samādapesi samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca vibhaṅgañca abhāsī”ti? ",
          "en": "“But in what way were you inspiring the mendicants with a talk on the recitation passage and analysis of One Fine Night?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:3.1",
          "pli": "“Evaṃ kho ahaṃ, bhante, bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassesiṃ samādapesiṃ samuttejesiṃ sampahaṃsesiṃ, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca vibhaṅgañca abhāsiṃ—",
          "en": "“I was doing so in this way, sir,” replied Ānanda. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:3.2",
          "pli": "Atītaṃ nānvāgameyya, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:3.3",
          "pli": "nappaṭikaṅkhe anāgataṃ; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:3.4",
          "pli": "Yadatītaṃ pahīnaṃ taṃ, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:3.5",
          "pli": "appattañca anāgataṃ. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:3.6",
          "pli": "Paccuppannañca yo dhammaṃ, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:3.7",
          "pli": "tattha tattha vipassati; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:3.8",
          "pli": "Asaṃhīraṃ asaṅkuppaṃ, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:3.9",
          "pli": "taṃ vidvā manubrūhaye. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:3.10",
          "pli": "Ajjeva kiccamātappaṃ, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:3.11",
          "pli": "ko jaññā maraṇaṃ suve; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:3.12",
          "pli": "Na hi no saṅgaraṃ tena, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:3.13",
          "pli": "mahāsenena maccunā. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:3.14",
          "pli": "Evaṃvihāriṃ ātāpiṃ, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:3.15",
          "pli": "ahorattamatanditaṃ; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:3.16",
          "pli": "Taṃ ve bhaddekarattoti, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:3.17",
          "pli": "santo ācikkhate muni. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:4.1",
          "pli": "‘Kathañca, āvuso, atītaṃ anvāgameti? ",
          "en": "(And he went on to repeat the verses and analysis as in the previous discourse, MN 131.) "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:4.2",
          "pli": "Evaṃrūpo ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti, evaṃvedano ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti, evaṃsañño ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti, evaṃsaṅkhāro ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti, evaṃviññāṇo ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti—",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:4.3",
          "pli": "evaṃ kho, āvuso, atītaṃ anvāgameti. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:5.1",
          "pli": "Kathañca, āvuso, atītaṃ nānvāgameti? ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:5.2",
          "pli": "Evaṃrūpo ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti, evaṃvedano ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti, evaṃsañño ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti, evaṃsaṅkhāro ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti, evaṃviññāṇo ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti—",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:5.3",
          "pli": "evaṃ kho, āvuso, atītaṃ nānvāgameti. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:6.1",
          "pli": "Kathañca, āvuso, anāgataṃ paṭikaṅkhati? ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:6.2",
          "pli": "Evaṃrūpo siyaṃ anāgatamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti, evaṃvedano siyaṃ … pe … ",
          "en": " "
        },
