        {
          "scid": "mn132:8.2",
          "pli": "Idha, āvuso, assutavā puthujjano ariyānaṃ adassāvī ariyadhammassa akovido ariyadhamme avinīto sappurisānaṃ adassāvī sappurisadhammassa akovido sappurisadhamme avinīto ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
