        {
          "scid": "mn132:11.1",
          "pli": "Evaṃ kho ahaṃ, bhante, bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassesiṃ samādapesiṃ samuttejesiṃ sampahaṃsesiṃ, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca vibhaṅgañca abhāsin”ti. ",
          "en": "“That’s how I was inspiring the mendicants with a talk on the recitation passage and analysis of One Fine Night.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:11.2",
          "pli": "“Sādhu sādhu, ānanda. ",
          "en": "“Good, good, Ānanda. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "mn132:11.3",
          "pli": "Sādhu kho tvaṃ, ānanda, bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassesi samādapesi samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca vibhaṅgañca abhāsi: ",
          "en": "It’s good that you were inspiring the mendicants with a talk on the recitation passage and analysis of One Fine Night.” "
        },
        {
